# Authentication vs Authorization Examples

| Action | Authentication | Authorization |
|----------|----------------|---------------|
| Login | ✅ | ❌ |
| Enter Password | ✅ | ❌ |
| Access Dashboard | ❌ | ✅ |
| Delete User | ❌ | ✅ |
| View Own Profile | ❌ | ✅ |
| Change Website Settings | ❌ | ✅ |

